##################################
#####     YAY CHEATSHEET     #####
##################################

# SET COLOR OUTOUT
vim /etc/pacman.conf
'Color Option'





# 
Present package-installation selection menu: yay <Search Term>

Install dependencies and build a local PKGBUILD: yay -Bi <dir>

Download PKGBUILD from ABS or AUR: yay -G <AUR Package>

Print to stdout PKGBUILD from ABS or AUR: yay -Gp <AUR Package>

Print system statistics: yay -Ps

Perform system upgrade, but also check for development package updates: yay -Syu --devel






Clean unneeded dependencies: yay -Yc
